Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.86,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.11,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:22.45,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:47.93,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.93,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're fine, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.70,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.46,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:28.06,EP-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur8\fscx80\fscy80\fad(486,0)\t(0,1028,\blur0\fscx100\fscy100\shad3)\t(1029,1030,\bord0.1)\t(1653,3989,\shad12\blur5)\pos(625,514)}The Crystal Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.72,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.58,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.16,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Rainbow High...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:46.55,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: Nijikou (虹校) is an abbreviation for 虹陵館学園, the school the main characters attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.62,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.55,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you two are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,There's no secret tricks behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.99,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I am Misuzu Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:01.17,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,A senior at Rainbow High.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.14,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kakeru Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:03.99,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.59,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuka Minase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,We're both sophomores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.61,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.72,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.60,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.30,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.19,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I only did what was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:18.90,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai, what exactly is this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.15,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.83,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing for certain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.80,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,This world was created by someone's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.39,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,so the scenery is the same, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.94,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It exists in a different space-time than the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.58,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A different space-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:40.59,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Why have we come to this... this Crimson Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.65,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.65,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bad name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.32,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the true intention, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.45,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that there's a meaning to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.03,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,and also a reason for being chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.98,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two also have some kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.41,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.52,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Something like what you have, Kusakabe-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.18,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.92,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.28,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.91,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.13,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka...{Shouldn't this just be "Yuka..." ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:16.61,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Rin. Pyou. Tou. Sha. Kai. Jin. Retsu. Zai. Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: She is chanting the {\i1}Kuji-in{\i0} (Nine Hand Seals), a specialized form of Buddhist meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.96,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Over there? As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:27.40,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That crystal tower is full of powerful energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:30.92,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps... that place could be the center of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.53,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You two should hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.83,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.66,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:39.96,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kusakabe-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.65,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you!{. . . because as the male lead I can't not go!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.53,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:45.29,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.43,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You, without any powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:52.95,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:06.95,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: Tachibana Dousetsu is the name of a samurai that wielded {\i1}Raikiri{\i0}, with which he used to slay a lightning god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:01.29,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Dousetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.96,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.54,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.66,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.92,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.42,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:48.07,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You two must flee until this Crimson Night is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.72,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,When will it end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.56,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the proof that it will ever end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:55.29,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,It may not end this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.85,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We might be in here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:02.76,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a chance of escape at that tower, then I want to go! {'of escape' not in TL but this is the only way to make sense (more likely than 'of survival', as per the context of his previous lines) of his sentence}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.15,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to help this girl? {damn 'sono' throws me off, they haven't even met lisette yet}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.17,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.74,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.12,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you run and hide, the result is the same, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.35,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.57,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't know what could be in that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.52,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,You may not be able to completely protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.50,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.88,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka, go somewhere and-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.09,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too, don't leave me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.49,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I will definitely protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.38,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:42.06,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.22,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:48.73,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.48,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,My eye...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.84,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Can you go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.88,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.92,Default,Enemy A,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let you proceed any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.68,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,So there's also ones that can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.33,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that you cannot let us pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.43,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,then that means you have something important to protect there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.10,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:41.83,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.74,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She doesn't have any wasted movements.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.35,Default,Enemy A,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, that girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.29,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.96,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.57,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.93,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.00,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lisette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.79,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you call out for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.51,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trapped in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:43.01,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,Save me... get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.22,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.10,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Lisette is the origin of the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:52.09,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, she's the person that made this Crimson Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.36,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Lisette?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.19,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:58.93,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.95,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.14,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.03,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Send us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.33,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,To the world where we came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.55,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.29,Default,Lisette,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.31,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.49,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's something inside of Lisette...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:23.38,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It unconsciously activated, created this world, and brought us into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.18,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.52,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.68,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,She's suffering. Please, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.40,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.28,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,What a weak boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.48,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,You're so similar to Verard Staich, yet so different. {tried to pick closest sounding german/hungarian/romanian de-romaji'd version of 'sutaiku'}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:13.69,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun... {Is this all she can say?}{pretty much}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:21.70,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:25.32,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,Within this palace, your skills are unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.04,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we have you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.93,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Are all of you those who protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Or those who rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:38.62,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need to answer "fragments" that will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.59,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,"Fragments"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:44.43,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,All of you must not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.76,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.77,Default,Enemy B,0000,0000,0000,,Invidia! {Insaido!}{G-Force sexiness-over-9000}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.40,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.33,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.65,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun! {Yep, apparantly it is all she can say :/ }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Didn't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to comfort you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so insincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.24,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.06,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.21,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,What about Minase-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.59,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.29,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I feel like I'm being toyed around with as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.07,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.26,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I didn't want to be chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.84,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Them."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You said it before, right? "Them."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.48,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that there are others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,people that were also brought into the Crimson Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.24,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.90,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, there are three others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.59,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,But I've only seen the face of one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:33.66,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The other two I caught a glimpse of as they were leaving, out of the corner of my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.27,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of people are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.08,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them are students at Rainbow High.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.84,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls and one guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.66,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Were they running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.70,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.82,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No, they were fighting with the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.68,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.13,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:53.34,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,In Onmyoudou, all wicked beings are called demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:56.23,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL NOTE: {\i1}Onmyoudou{\i0} is a practice of spiritual balance based on Wu Xing and Yin and Yang. An {\i1}Onmyouji{\i0} is a practitioner of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:56.23,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So you're an Onmyouji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.02,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,It's hereditary. {T Note: I don't think this is an actual word.}{fixed}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.98,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Those people were not shiki. {plural of shiki is shiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:04.44,Default,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL NOTE: {\i1}Shiki{\i0} are a type of spirit summoned by an {\i1}onmyouji{\i0}, often invisible to normal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:04.44,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... rather than demons, they are spirits of darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.15,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,An "Ahriman" might be more appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.10,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ahriman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.62,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Um... so where are the other students?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.00,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll let you meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:17.36,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,The one that I saw is a senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.50,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I also know her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.08,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If they were fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.15,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,do they have some kind of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.63,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So, are they also Onmyouji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.68,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:30.09,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,About their powers, it'd be better to ask them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.31,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have some kind of power too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.80,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:40.43,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, that black knight said that I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:49.61,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki-kun, can you try taking that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.45,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,My right eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:58.37,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really certain, but you remember the pain back then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:04.04,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, right. Now that you mention it, whenever we enter the Crimson Night, my right eye always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.35,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.59,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.81,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.79,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.99,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,Minase-kun, don't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:26.92,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:30.53,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,I see... that's enough, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.15,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You probably haven't awakened yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.38,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what kind of power it has...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.53,Default,Misuzu Kusakabe,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I will find out as much as I can about that eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.97,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I also have some kind of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.89,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,So that means that I also have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.71,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were chosen, right? Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.48,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if we stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.34,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.87,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,When I die, stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:16.79,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.35,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.63,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.98,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:22.91,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I will, for sure. {@RC: any synonyms you want here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:38.46,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,I found Kakeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:41.44,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, crossing arms like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.92,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,All lovey dovey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.02,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tadashi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.91,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I couldn't stop him in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.32,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.32,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Aw geez, what the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall over all of a sudden! I hit my head, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.78,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, I hit my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.74,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,How exactly could you have hit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.81,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.14,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.73,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.36,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:09.96,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.23,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Am I some kind of domestic animal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.06,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.01,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.20,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:34.90,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I brought her because she asked me to guide her through Shin-Ayame, but she disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.22,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.54,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.04,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Or you can ignore me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.40,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go? We were looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.09,Default,Shiori Momono,0000,0000,0000,,I was following a cat, then I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.95,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.33,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, lift me up! For two cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.73,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're really annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.09,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be picked up, then give me a Yuki-ccho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:02.17,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: She's making a reference to the man on the 10,000 yen bill (Yukichi Fukuzawa).
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.17,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,You're a demon bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:04.06,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a {\i1}bride{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.02,Default,Kaori Natsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be your bride?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.02,Default,Tadashi Teruya,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have them give me a break from work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.42,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,After I greet the master, I'll walk you back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.41,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.51,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.29,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.96,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.96,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you're a new part-timer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:40.34,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I believe that the master will be back from shopping soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.60,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:45.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but have we met you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:49.53,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we might have, because we go to the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.74,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:19:00.19,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I had an accident earlier. I'm quite the klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:03.53,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm all right, so no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:10.22,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Kouryoukan Academy freshman in class C. My name is Yukiko Hirohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:10.22,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TL Note: Nijikouryoukan-Gakuen (虹陵館学園) is the full name of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.83,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Yuki-pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.79,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-pon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.11,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:20.40,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I call Satsuki-senpai and Minase-senpai by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.63,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't "Satsuki-senpai" all right, as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:24.90,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.42,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, it'd be like we're strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.57,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,We {\i1}are{\i0} strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.34,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.29,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.93,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Yuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.56,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Affirmative. {roger}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:38.19,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. I'll call Minase-senpai "Yuka-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.78,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,And Satsuki-senpai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.19,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-cchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.41,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least call me Kakeru-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.70,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, affirmative!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.92,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, that's what it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:48.79,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll pour you some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:53.49,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko special! I just perfected it a while ago, it's really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.00,Default,Yukiko Hirohara,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.39,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,After talking with Yukiko-chan, it's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:11.28,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I already called Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.35,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:15.97,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll go home for today. I'm tired, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:16.98,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.51,0:20:20.57,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that we're the only ones having hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.90,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.82,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That was just an illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.33,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,Kukuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.63,Default,Yuka Minase,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's better not to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.59,Default,Kakeru Satsuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so, thanks.
